article_id:2301,category_name:News,title_name:Announcing a Platinum Showcase! 5★ Dragon Guaranteed!,image_path:,message:<div>A Platinum Showcase starts on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1625464800"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>The Platinum Showcase is a limited summon showcase that works similarly to a tenfold summon in that one summon will get you 10 results. The difference between a regular tenfold summon and this Platinum Showcase is that a 5★ dragon is guaranteed to appear.</div><div><br></div><div>During the availability period, players are limited to doing the Platinum Showcase summon two times, and these summons can only be performed with diamantium (purchase required).</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Note: The newly added adventurer from the Toll of the Deep summon showcase, which starts at the same time, is not included in the roster for this summon showcase.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for the Platinum Showcase:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1625464800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1626328799"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the 5★ dragons eligible to appear as the guaranteed 5★ summon.</div><div><br></div><div>5★ dragons eligible for guaranteed appearance as the 10th summon:</div><div>
