			</dt>
			<dd><div>Deals water damage to enemies in a line.<br>Damage will be increased based on the number<br>of Ice Spirit stacks the user has. Ice Spirit stacks<br>are gained through Styx's normal attacks, and can<br>stack up to three times. All Ice Spirit stacks<br>will be consumed when the user uses this skill,<br>or when their shapeshift is undone.</div></dd></dl></div><div class="ability explanation">
